Name: Run Jump Die Repeat
About the game: Run Jump Die Repeat is a single button platformer game. Press SPACE to run, bounce, jump, climb, and kill as you attempt to save the Cracker Princess and escape the evil Cron Rebels home planet. Featuring: 50 increasingly challenging levels 3 different game modes to play (story, classic, hardcore) Simple yet engaging story mode One button controls you'll have to learn to master Death.. lots of deaths x_x
